1. Go to the [Vercel website](https://vercel.com/) and log in or sign up if you don't have an account.
2. Click on "New Project" and select "Import Git Repository."
3. Choose your GitHub repository from the list.
4. When configuring the deployment settings, select the specific branch you want to deploy.
5. Click "Deploy."
6. Wait for the deployment process to complete. Your app will be live on a Vercel URL.
